<i>noun</i>: 폭주 [폭쭈], 수마 [수마], 대홍수 [대ː홍수] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭주 [폭쭈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. downpour; raining hard</dd><br>
<dd>비가 갑자기 많이 쏟아짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of rain pouring down a lot suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rush; deluge</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 주문 등이 처리하기 힘들 정도로 한꺼번에 몰림.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of many tasks, orders, etc., rushing in all at once, so that it is hard to handle them.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수마 [수마]</dt><br>
<dd>flood; deluge</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 심한 피해를 일으키는 장마나 홍수.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A disastrous monsoon or flood.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대홍수 [대ː홍수]</dt><br>
<dd>great flood; cataclysm; deluge</dd><br>
<dd>큰 홍수.</dd><br>
<dd>A huge flood.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>